<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="icons/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="icons/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="icons/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="manifest" href="icons/site.webmanifest">
    
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
    <script src="/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <style>
        .pagination-btn {
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            border: 1px solid #D1D5DB;
            border-radius: 0.375rem;
            background-color: white;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            transition: background-color 0.2s;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .pagination-btn:hover:not(:disabled) {
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
        }
        /* Scrollbar fina para tabelas e listas */
        ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #f1f1f1; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #888; border-radius: 3px; }
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #555; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    
    <header class="bg-white shadow-md border-b-2 border-gray-100 sticky top-0 z-40">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex justify-between items-center h-20">
            <a href="/"><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8c/SENAI_S%C3%A3o_Paulo_logo.png" alt="Logo SENAI" class="h-10"></a>
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-6">
                <a href="/gerenciamento" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-red-700 font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Gerenciamento
                </a>
                <a href="/perfil" class="text-gray-600 hover:text-red-700 font-semibold transition-colors duration-200 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">
                    Meu Perfil
                </a>
                <span class="text-gray-300">|</span>
                <span class="text-gray-700 hidden sm:inline">Bem-vindo, <strong class="text-red-700"><%= professorName %></strong>!</span>
                <a href="/logout" class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-md font-semibold text-center uppercase tracking-wider text-xs transition-transform duration-200 transform hover:scale-105 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 bg-red-700 text-white hover:bg-red-800 focus:ring-red-500">
                    Sair
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8 flex-grow w-full">
        <div class="space-y-8">
            <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-red-700 mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Exportar Relat칩rio Di치rio</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
                    Selecione a data para gerar um relat칩rio em PDF com os dados de atividade dos alunos.
                </p>
                <div class="flex items-end gap-4">
                    <div>
                        <label for="reportDate" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Data do Relat칩rio</label>
                        <input type="date" id="reportDate" class="mt-1 w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-600 outline-none">
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <button id="downloadPdfBtn" class="inline-block px-6 py-2.5 rounded-md font-semibold text-center uppercase tracking-wider text-sm bg-red-700 text-white hover:bg-red-800 transition">
                            Baixar Relat칩rio
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="reportError" class="text-red-600 text-sm mt-2"></div>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-red-700">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Filtros de Dados</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 items-end">
                    <div>
                        <label for="classSelect" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Filtrar por Turma</label>
                        <select id="classSelect" class="mt-1 w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-600 outline-none">
                            <option value="null">Vis칚o Geral (Todas as Turmas)</option>
                            <% if (classes.length > 0) { %>
                                <% classes.forEach(cls => { %>
                                    <option value="<%= cls.id %>"><%= cls.name %></option>
                                <% }) %>
                            <% } %>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <label for="search-input" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Pesquisar</label>
                        <input type="text" id="search-input" placeholder="Aluno, ID ou URL" class="mt-1 w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-600 outline-none">
                    </div>
                    
                    <div>
                        <label for="category-select" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700">Categoria</label>
                        <select id="category-select" class="mt-1 w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-600 outline-none">
                            <option value="">Todas</option>
                            <% categories.forEach(cat => { %>
                                <option value="<%= cat %>"><%= cat %></option>
                            <% }) %>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-2"> 
                        <div class="flex items-center">
                            <input id="show-alerts-checkbox" type="checkbox" class="h-4 w-4 text-red-600 border-gray-300 rounded focus:ring-red-500">
                            <label for="show-alerts-checkbox" class="ml-2 block text-sm text-gray-900">Apenas Alertas</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex gap-2">
                            <button id="apply-filters-btn" class="flex-1 px-4 py-2 rounded-md font-bold text-sm bg-red-700 text-white hover:bg-red-800 transition">Filtrar</button>
                            <button id="clear-filters-btn" class="flex-1 px-4 py-2 rounded-md font-bold text-sm bg-gray-600 text-white hover:bg-gray-700 transition">Limpar</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div id="dashboard-content" class="space-y-8">
                
                <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-red-700">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Resumo de Atividade</h2>
                        <button onclick="openTutorialModal()" class="w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full text-white bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 font-extrabold text-lg shadow-md transition" title="Ver Tutorial">?</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-lg shadow border border-gray-200">
                        <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
                            <thead class="bg-gray-100 border-b border-gray-200">
                                <tr>
                                    <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider w-32">Alertas</th>
                                    <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider w-24">Status</th>
                                    <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Aluno / ID</th>
                                    <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Tempo Total</th>
                                    <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">A칞칫es</th>
                                    <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">칔ltimo Log</th>
                                </tr>
                            </thead>
                           <tbody id="usersTableBody" class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200"></tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-red-700">
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">An치lise Visual (Top 10 Sites)</h2>
                        <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                            <button class="chart-btn active bg-red-700 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm" data-type="bar">Barras</button>
                            <button class="chart-btn bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm hover:bg-gray-300" data-type="pie">Pizza</button>
                            <button class="chart-btn bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm hover:bg-gray-300" data-type="doughnut">Rosca</button>
                            <button class="chart-btn bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 px-3 py-1 rounded text-sm hover:bg-gray-300" data-type="line">Linha</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative h-80 w-full">
                        <canvas id="mainChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </section>
                
                <section class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-red-700">
                    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Logs de Atividade (<span id="logs-count">0</span>)</h2>
                    <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-lg shadow border border-gray-200 max-h-[600px] overflow-y-auto">
                        <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-200">
                           <thead class="bg-gray-50 sticky top-0">
                               <tr>
                                   <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Aluno</th>
                                   <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">URL</th>
                                   <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Dura칞칚o</th>
                                   <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Categoria</th>
                                   <th class="px-6 py-3 text-left text-xs font-medium text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Hora</th>
                               </tr>
                           </thead>
                           <tbody id="logsTableBody" class="bg-white divide-y divide-gray-200"></tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    <div id="logs-pagination-container"></div>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-red-800 text-white mt-auto">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-sm">춸 <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> SENAI -  Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
    
    <%- include('partials/modals') %>

    <div id="categoryEditModal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-50 overflow-y-auto h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center z-50">
        <div class="relative mx-auto p-6 border w-full max-w-md shadow-xl rounded-lg bg-white transform transition-all">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-4">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Corrigir Categoria</h3>
                    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Ajude a IA a classificar melhor este site.</p>
                </div>
                <button id="closeCategoryModalX" type="button" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 focus:outline-none">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path></svg>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-3 rounded border border-gray-200 mb-4">
                <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase">Site:</p>
                <p id="modalUrlDisplay" class="text-sm font-mono text-blue-600 font-bold break-all"></p>
            </div>
    
            <div id="modalCategoryList" class="space-y-1 max-h-60 overflow-y-auto mb-6 pr-2 border-t border-b py-2">
            </div>
    
            <div class="flex justify-end gap-3 pt-2">
                <button id="cancelCategoryModalBtn" type="button" class="px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-gray-300 text-gray-700 rounded hover:bg-gray-50 transition">Cancelar</button>
                <button id="confirmCategoryChangeBtn" type="button" class="px-4 py-2 bg-red-700 text-white font-bold rounded hover:bg-red-800 shadow transition">Salvar & Aprender</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="alertLogsModal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-50 overflow-y-auto h-full w-full flex items-center justify-center z-50">
        <div class="relative mx-auto p-6 border w-full max-w-2xl shadow-xl rounded-lg bg-white">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
                <h3 id="alertLogsTitle" class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900">Logs de Alerta</h3>
                <button onclick="closeAlertLogsModal()" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 text-2xl font-bold">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <div id="alertLogsContainer" class="max-h-[400px] overflow-y-auto border rounded">
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 flex justify-end">
                <button onclick="closeAlertLogsModal()" class="px-4 py-2 bg-gray-600 text-white rounded hover:bg-gray-700">Fechar</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="tutorialModal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-gray-900 bg-opacity-75 flex items-center justify-center z-50">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl w-full max-w-lg p-6 relative">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-700 mb-4">Como usar o Painel</h2>
            
            <div id="step-1" class="tour-step">
                <p class="mb-4">1. Use os filtros no topo para selecionar uma <strong>Data</strong> e uma <strong>Turma</strong>.</p>
                <img src="https://placehold.co/400x150?text=Filtros+de+Data+e+Turma" class="w-full rounded border mb-4">
            </div>
            <div id="step-2" class="tour-step hidden">
                <p class="mb-4">2. Na tabela de resumo, alunos com 游댮 acessaram sites proibidos (Jogos, Redes Sociais). Clique no 칤cone para ver os detalhes.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="step-3" class="tour-step hidden">
                <p class="mb-4">3. Se a categoria de um site estiver errada, clique nela na lista de logs para corrigir. A IA aprender치 com sua corre칞칚o!</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mt-6">
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-500">Passo <span id="currentStep">1</span> de 3</span>
                <div class="flex gap-2">
                    <button id="prevStepBtn" onclick="prevStep()" class="hidden px-3 py-1 text-gray-600 border rounded hover:bg-gray-100">Anterior</button>
                    <button id="nextStepBtn" onclick="nextStep()" class="px-3 py-1 bg-red-700 text-white rounded hover:bg-red-800">Pr칩ximo</button>
                    <button id="finishTourBtn" onclick="closeTutorialModal()" class="hidden px-3 py-1 bg-green-600 text-white rounded hover:bg-green-700">Entendi</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button onclick="closeTutorialModal()" class="absolute top-2 right-2 text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-600 text-xl">&times;</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>